headline: Oklahoma Sports Hall of Fame and Jim Thorpe Association Proudly Reveal the Paycom Jim Thorpe Award 2025 Preseason Watch List
summary: OKLAHOMA CITY, July 30, 2025--Today, Oklahoma Sports Hall of Fame (OSHOF) and Jim Thorpe Association released the prestigious Paycom Jim Thorpe Award Preseason Watch List. This list includes 35 of the nation’s best defensive backs, representing nine conferences and one independent university. headline: Paycom unveils IWant: Command-driven AI engine with accurate, rapid results
summary: OKLAHOMA CITY, July 30, 2025--Paycom Software, Inc. (NYSE: PAYC) ("Paycom"), a leading provider of comprehensive, cloud-based human capital management software, today announced the launch of IWant, the industry’s first command-driven AI engine that revolutionizes the way all users navigate and access their information within a single database.
